Package: landscapeR
Title: Comparative Decomposition and State-Transition Dynamics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Denis", "O'Meally", email = "denis@omeally.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5095-4109"))
Description: S4-based pipeline combining GSVD/HO-GSVD comparative decomposition
    with quasi-potential state-transition modelling on multi-layer omic data.
    Provides a contract/registry architecture for synthetic validation (Stage 0),
    archetype classification (Stage 0.5), distributional fit assessment (Stage 0.75),
    decomposition (Stage 1), and dynamics estimation (Stage 2).
